MBOMBELA &#8211; Today marks the last day of a three-day cultural festival that embraces the rich and vibrant cultures of our province. The Mpumalanga Cultural Festival will conclude with a 16-hour marathon concert at the Mbombela stadium.&nbsp;The experience carnival started with a parade btween the City Centre and Promenade Centre on Thursday.Read more here: Entertainment spectacle to dazzle the city Since then, Mbombela was abuzz with people enjoying different cultural performances of the province and those from our neighbouring countries Swaziland and Mozambique.&nbsp;